ntent/uploads/2013/02/DSC7206-146x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="DSC7206" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7206-146x200.jpg 146w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7206-562x768.jpg 562w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7206-270x368.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7206.jpg 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 146px) 100vw, 146px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7212-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="DSC7212" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7212-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7212-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7212-270x179.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="193" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7287-290x193.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="DSC7287" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7287-290x193.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7287-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/DSC7287-270x179.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li></ul></div></div></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p> <a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/ancona-teatro-delle-muse-madama-butterfly/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/ancona-teatro-delle-muse-madama-butterfly/#comments">2 Replies</a></div><div class="entr