ww.gbopera.it/tag/alessandro-pucci/" rel="tag">alessandro pucci</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/aliona-staricova/" rel="tag">aliona staricova</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/arnaud-bernard/" rel="tag">Arnaud Bernard</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/elena-popovskaya/" rel="tag">elena popovskaya</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/enkelejida-shkosa/" rel="tag">enkelejida shkosa</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giacomo-puccini/" rel="tag">Giacomo Puccini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gianfranco-montresor/" rel="tag">Gianfranco Montresor</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gianni-paci/" rel="tag">gianni paci</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/luciano-ganci/" rel="tag">Luciano Ganci</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/madama-butterfly/" rel="tag">Madama Butterfly</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/renato-palumbo/" rel="tag">Renato Palumbo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-delle-muse-di-ancona/" rel="tag">Teatro delle Muse di Ancona</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="alessandro pucci, aliona staricova, Arnaud Bernard, elena popovskaya, enkelejida shkosa, Giacomo Puccini, Gianfranco Montresor, gianni paci, Luciano Ganci, Madama Butterfly, Opera lirica, Renato Palumbo, Teatro delle Muse di Ancona"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/a482ad643dfdd4893232b5c8887b9fbf" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/IMG_3710-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Davide Oliviero" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Davide Olivier